dct_title_s: Coulterville route from Merced to Yosemite
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Numbered 135 in lower left corner, 3 in upper left and 58 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
